  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ContentAttached
    Interface for attaching arbitrary content to an object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Content
    A generic class for holding arbitrary binary data.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicateException
    Throw a DuplicateException when duplicate data is detected while processing.
    MalformedException
    Throw a MalformedException when data is malformed.
    StrictException
    Throw a StrictException to indicate that a process or data has failed to meet requirements.
    UnsupportedException
    Throw a UnsupportedException to indicate that the provided data is not supported.
    ValidationException
    Throw a ValidationException when data fails validation.
